T1  - Measuring outward orientation in LDCs: Can it be done?
AU  - Pritchett, Lant
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 49
IS  - 2
SP  - 307
EP  - 335
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/05/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
